0:
”Alexa, ask Manor Info what is for lunch today.”
”Alexa, ask Manor Info what is for lunch this week.”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: manor info
des:
This Manor Info skill gives you unofficial information about different aspects of the Honeoye Falls Lima Intermediate School. 
You can ask Manor Info what is for lunch today or tomorrow, or for the week, when the next day off from school is, as well as when the last day of school is. 

Ask Manor Info for help for a list of available options.
This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by the Honeoye Falls Lima School District.
priv:

The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
